node.text:
what to do with it. I would get it, and then in less than a week, it was just . . . GONE! Those days were challenging, embarrassing and frustrating.
 
This is why I wanted to spend a whole episode talking about 10 things to NOT do when we get our paycheck. (Believe me, I’ve done some STUPID stuff with my paycheck, and I wish someone had told me this sooner.) Go check out the full episode to learn how to avoid those money mistakes so you can start stacking some serious cash.
 
Click the link in my bio.

node.text:
👋🏾 I’m back! I am refreshed, renewed and ready to attack the second part of this year. Over the last 14 days, I’ve spent some time with my mentor @dhariusdaniels, my therapist and close friends. 
 
The best part of my 14 days was that 7 of them were spent in the beautiful city of Cancún, Mexico at my new favorite resort @atelierplayamujeres. This 5 star all-inclusive resort was exactly what I needed—from reading my word on the rooftop of my room every morning, to playing golf on their private golf course, to swimming in the resort's private VIP rooftop pool. And their food and hospitality was incredible. 
 
So you see why I’m smiling in my first picture! Back to talking about building WEALTH without DEBT tomorrow. I am so pumped, WE are going higher TOGETHER.

node.text:
T H I R T Y - S E V E N 🎉 Today I am saying hello to chapter 37 of my life and closing chapter 36. I woke up this morning thanking God for another year. Chapter 36 taught me a lot about me—things that I DO NOT like, things I LOVE, and things I can improve on.

I’m starting Chapter 37 with a sabbatical for two weeks. While on sabbatical, I’m going to be redefining what success looks like for ANTHONY and not the WORLD.

This year, I’m going to be more 𝐅𝐎𝐂𝐔𝐒𝐄𝐃 & 𝐃𝐄𝐓𝐄𝐑𝐌𝐈𝐍𝐄𝐃 in four areas of my life: strengthening my spiritual walk, evolving my MINDSET, building a healthier NETWORK (relationships), and growing my NET WORTH. I’m working on something special around this and can’t wait to share it with YOU!

My prayer for chapter 37 is that I will grow closer to God, meet my wife, have more peace, help people build TRUE wealth while continuing to build my own, experience more happy times, and surround myself with more people who truly love me.

So . . . starting tonight at midnight, July 2nd through July 15th, I will be unplugging from social media and not posting anything. That means no Instagram, YouTube, Clubhouse, Twitter or Facebook. We’ll be releasing something MAJOR when I return, but until then, pray for ya boy as I allow God to refresh and renew my mind.

Thank you to everyone who sent me a birthday text, phone call, DM or cash app ($DebtFreeAO). 😁❤️
⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
See you on July 16th! 

Photographer: @sethfarmerphotography 
Styled by: @jdfrierson 
Hair cut: @huntdabarber
👖& 👞: @asos

Photo by A N T H O N Y  O ‘ N E A L on June 30, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'We're praying for a small business.'.
